    Weights 1.0,1.0
EndFeature

# Water oxygen
DefineFeature WaterNuclGroup [O;v2;H2]
    Family Nucleophile
    Weights 1.0
EndFeature

# Sulfonyl and Sulfinyl-like oxygen: C2S=O
DefineFeature SulfurNuclGroup [$(O=[S;v4,v6]([#6])[#6])]=[$([S;v4,v6]([#6])([#6])=O)]
